at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.network

Class Keywords

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.network.Keywords

  • public class Keywords
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds all the keywords that are to be used to communicate with other devices (via JSON-strings).
    The keywords should be accessed in a static manner (without instantiation of this class), which is why the constructor has been set private.
    Author:
    Boeck
